  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Suntech Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As a result of the Project, Suntech is expected to (i) continue to produce solar panels over the life of the Project which should reduce CO2 by 93 million tons over the modules usable lives, (ii) create up to 1,200 highly-skilled jobs including 360 jobs for women; and (iii) support the development of a solar power industry in China and globally, since Suntech is a leader in the solar sector.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC will provide a convertible loan of up to $100 million to support Suntechs 2009-2013 capital expenditure plans and debt refinancing requirements.</narrative>
  </description>
